quran[26]{c,v,t}:
  56,51,"Afei mo ayerafoͻ no a mofaa (nokorε no) nkontompo no,"
  56,52,"Mobɛdidi afiri dua Zaqqum so,"
  56,53,"Na mode ahyε (mo) afru ma,"
  56,54,"Na moanom nsuo hyeε agu so;"
  56,55,"Na (mo) bεnom no sεdeε yoma a sukͻm de no renom nsuo."
  56,56,"Woi na εbεyε wͻn brεsuo a yεde bεma wͻn akwaaba wͻ (daakye) akatua Da no."
  56,57,"Yεn na Yεbͻͻ mo na afei adεn nti na monye nnie?"
  56,58,"Moahunu (ahobaeε) a mohwie gu (ͻbaa awodeε mu) no?"
  56,59,"Mo na mobͻ (akͻdaa no) anaasε Yε ne Ɔbͻͻ Adeε no?"
  56,60,"Yεn na Yɛahyehyε owuo de ato mo soͻ; na entumi mmu mfa Yεn so-"
  56,61,"-Sε Yεbεsesa mo tebea yi abͻ mo akͻ (tebea foforͻ) a mo nnim mu."
  56,62,"Ampa sε, monim mmͻeε a edi kan no; afei adεn na monfa nkͻ adwen-dwene mu?"
  56,63,"Moahunu (nneεma) a modua no?"
  56,64,"Mo na moma no fifiri na enyin, anaasε Yεn na Yεma no fifiri na enyin?"
  56,65,"Sε Yεpε a anka Yεbεma no ayam (anaasε Yεbεma no asεe) ama mo atwa adwo-"
  56,66,"(Ama moasu sε): “Nokorε yɛabͻ ka.”"
  56,67,"Aane, yɛahwere (y’agyapadeε)."
  56,68,"Moahunu nsuo a monom no?"
  56,69,"Mo na mosiane firi mununkum no mu ba, anaasε Yεn na Yɛsiane ba?"
  56,70,"Sε Yεpε a anka Yεbεma no ayε nkyene-nkyene. Adεn na afei monna (Nyankopͻn) aseε?"
  56,71,"Moahunu egya a mosͻ no?"
  56,72,"Mona mobͻ ne nnua no anaasε Yεn na Yεbͻeε?"
  56,73,"Yɛayε egya no nkaeε (a mode bεkae Amanehunu gya no), εsan nso wͻ mfasoͻ de ma onipa biara a ohia gya, ne εserε so akwantufoͻ no."
  56,74,"Enti bͻ wo Wura Nyankopͻn Kεseε no abodin."
  56,75,"Mede faako a nsoromma kͻtͻ di nse!"
  56,76,"Nokorε sε, εyε nsedie a εso paa sε anka monim a."
